"title": "6628: conversion, God's demands for",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6628: conversion, god's demands for",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Through his servants, God calls people to turn to him. He wants to save the world which is alienated from him, and to restore those of his backslidden people who return to him and renew their commitment to the covenant.</p>\n<h2>The need for conversion</h2>\n<h3>The world is alienated from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:21–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28\">ROM 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:11-Rom3:12\">ROM 3:11–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:3\">PSA 14:3</a></p>\n<h3>The world does not know God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:8\">GAL 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:34\">1CO 15:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:5\">1TH 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8\">2TH 1:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's people have turned away from him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:7\">MAL 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:43\">NUM 14:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:12\">DEU 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:11\">1SA 15:11</a> <em>Saul</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:9\">1KI 11:9</a> <em>Solomon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:27\">2CH 25:27</a> <em>Amaziah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:5\">JER 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:9\">EZK 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:11\">DAN 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:39\">ACT 7:39</a></p>\n<h2>God's demands for the conversion of all people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:22\">ISA 45:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:5\">PSA 65:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:11\">JON 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's demands for the conversion of his own people</h2>\n<h3>God's desire to save his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:11\">EZK 33:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:22\">JER 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:12-Joel2:13\">JOL 2:12–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:3\">ZEC 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's faithfulness to his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:14\">JER 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:40-Lev26:42\">LEV 26:40–26:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:9\">2CH 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:5\">HOS 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:1-Hos6:3\">HOS 6:1–6:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's promise of restoration</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:13-2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:13–7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:48-1Kgs8:49\">1KI 8:48–8:49</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:38-2Chr6:39\">2CH 6:38–6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:9\">NEH 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>The call to conversion through God's servants</h2>\n<h3>The encouragement of his leaders</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14-Josh24:15\">JOS 24:14–24:15</a> <em>Joshua</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:17\">2KI 11:17</a> <em>Jehoida</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:24-2Kgs23:25\">2KI 23:24–23:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:31-2Chr34:33\">2CH 34:31–34:33</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:11-2Chr15:15\">2CH 15:11–15:15</a> <em>Asa</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:4\">2CH 19:4</a> <em>Jehoshaphat</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:6-2Chr29:10\">2CH 29:6–29:10</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:13\">PSA 51:13</a> <em>David</em></p>\n<h3>The ministry of his prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:15\">JER 35:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:19\">2CH 24:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:4\">JER 25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:1-Hos14:2\">HOS 14:1–14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:2\">JON 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>The preaching of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:16-Acts26:18\">ACT 26:16–26:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:14–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a></p>\n<h2>Rejection of God's call to conversion</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:13\">ISA 9:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:10\">JER 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:4\">HOS 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:10\">HOS 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:6-Amos4:11\">AMO 4:6–4:11</a></p>",
